<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #111827;">
  <h2 style="color:#111827;margin-top:0;">New appointment request received</h2>

  <p>Hi {{#if doctorName}}{{doctorName}}{{else}}Doctor{{/if}},</p>

  <p>
    You have received a new appointment request from
    <strong>{{#if patientName}}{{patientName}}{{else}}a patient{{/if}}</strong>
    for
    <strong>{{appointmentDateTime}}</strong>.
  </p>

  {{#if appointmentNumber}}
    <p>
      Appointment number:
      <strong>{{appointmentNumber}}</strong>.
    </p>
  {{/if}}

  <p>
    Please review this appointment in the Remedy portal and take action (accept
    or reject) as soon as possible.
  </p>

  <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:18px;">Best regards,<br />The Remedy Team</p>
</div>